title: Chinese suppliers make up majority of Vision Pro supply chain, say sources
text: Credit: AFP Chinese suppliers command most of the supply chain for Apple's new Vision Pro spatial computer, while suppliers from the US, Japan, and South Korea retain control of critical components, according to industry sources.
